stories.title: U.S. Loses Bid to Extradite Young Briton in Crypto Hacking Case

stories.text:
Hey HN Folks,

Apple is currently showing my cell phone and info on a business I was previously involved with a marker at my home address. They seemly got the data without my permission from a data broker.

I have previously asked Apple to remove the historical business details from Apple Maps via the built in feedback form and via email.

The place was removed for a short period of time but today I discovered the place is back and Apple are now publishing my mobile cell number on the same place marker!

Contacting tier 1 support is going to be comical at best. Does anyone have any thoughts on how to fix this?
